  <h2>What we are</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>A <strong>guide</strong> and set of free browser-based tools</li>
    <li>Focused on plain English, public data, and honest outcomes</li>
    <li>Built for both uninsured patients and insured people decoding EOBs</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>What we are not</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Not a law firm, medical practice, or insurance broker</li>
    <li>Not a bill negotiation service (we may link to resources)</li>
    <li>Not a source of guaranteed savings or fraud accusations</li>
